          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/ing-words-scrabble-bingo/" class="block p-5 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10 hover:border-purple-400 transition-all group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 text-purple-400 text-lg">✨</span>
          <div>
