      <a href="/blog/six-letter-words-that-lead-to-bingos/" class="block p-5 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10 hover:border-purple-400 transition-all group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 text-purple-400 text-lg">🪜</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors">Six-Letter Words That Lead to Bingos</h3>
