          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Section: Training & Recognition -->
    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Training & Recognition</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4">Speed is everything under tournament clock pressure — train your brain to spot bingo patterns instantly.</p>

    <div class="grid gap-4 not-prose">
      <a href="/blog/bingo-training-methods/" class="block p-5 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10 hover:border-cyan-400 transition-all group">
